snippet.title: Late Night Trash Can with Amber Ruffin and Jenny Hagel Live at SXSW
snippet.description:
Late Night writers Amber Ruffin and Jenny Hagel share their rejected Late Night ideas live at South by Southwest. The Late Night Podcast is released every Wednesday and Friday on Apple Podcasts, TuneIn, Stitcher or wherever you listen to podcasts.
» Subscribe to Late Night: http://bit.ly/LateNightSeth
» Get more Late Night with Seth Meyers: http://www.nbc.com/late-night-with-seth-meyers/
» Watch Late Night with Seth Meyers Weeknights 12:35/11:35c on NBC.
